{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128757, "create_time": 1653052707, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "正常情况下经济增速和失业率负相关，中国的经济增速和失业率完全不相关，所以中国的经济增速和失业率其中必定至少有一个是假的", "timestamp": 1653052707}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128761, "create_time": 1653052821, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "先问是不是，再问为什么。东北大部分地级市现在的GDP都低于2012年的水平", "timestamp": 1653052821}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128763, "create_time": 1653052885, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "至少疫情有没有清零是掩盖不了的，因为奥密克戎的高传播性决定了这个病毒藏不住的。要么真清零要么大爆发，不存在统计数据可以糊弄的中间状态。", "timestamp": 1653052885}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128766, "create_time": 1653052915, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 东北gdp年年正增长的，是经济普查砍掉的，这恰好说明了东北2010年左右gdp注水严重", "timestamp": 1653052915}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128771, "create_time": 1653053035, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "他们在污染汉语", "timestamp": 1653053035}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128792, "create_time": 1653054144, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "中国人口数据都能造假，还有什么不能造假的", "timestamp": 1653054144}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128812, "create_time": 1653054811, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Carol: “真清零”和“社会面清零”之间的差距是可以藏得住的。数据可以说每天新增都是管控人员，社会面没有新增，但是，全部人口中有百分之多少被管控了，是从来不说的。很显然，只要把所有人都管控起来，就能实现社会面清零", "timestamp": 1653054811}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128819, "create_time": 1653054958, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 政府太狗了", "timestamp": 1653054958}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128831, "create_time": 1653055376, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Francis: 管控不需要行政成本？真以为政府是利维坦有无限的控制能力想封就封？封控影响的不是官员考核最看重GDP成长数据？", "timestamp": 1653055376}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128836, "create_time": 1653055503, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 对于政府，很多目标是比经济发展更重要的，经济搞不好，最多影响官员升迁，但是计划生育搞不好，计生办的官员是要处罚的，防疫搞不好，比如湖北的F4，是会被撤职的", "timestamp": 1653055503}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128848, "create_time": 1653055772, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Carol: 经济搞不好，可能会导致难以升迁，而抗疫搞不好，一定会导致直接就地免职。如果是你，你怎么选", "timestamp": 1653055772}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128877, "create_time": 1653056407, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Francis: 所以为啥最上面会制定这样的考核指标呢？如果放开疫情控制可以有利于整体的经济的话，完全找不出他们图一个抗疫虚名的动机，毕竟他们的位子又不是靠民意获取，没有选举政绩的压力。", "timestamp": 1653056407}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128882, "create_time": 1653056541, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 国家间政治体系优越性的比较，想证明的是共产党领导的优越性，和底层人民无关", "timestamp": 1653056541}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128900, "create_time": 1653057005, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 优越性指的大概是“中华民族伟大复兴”吧，经济是其中最核心的指标，如果能够提升经济，我觉得他们完全不在乎躺平多死几百万人。", "timestamp": 1653057005}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128908, "create_time": 1653057139, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 确实不在乎，烟草每年死一百多万也没人关心过；但是优越性不仅是经济，看看这个文章 http://www.qstheory.cn/dukan/qs/2020-06/16/c_1126112345.htm", "timestamp": 1653057139}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128918, "create_time": 1653057484, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以最上面的人在乎的是舆论宣传中营造的虚无缥缈的优势？不至于吧，这套体制最大的特点是阴晴不定，政策随着最高层的意思说变就变，完全看不出最上层受制于下面舆论宣传的地方，反而是下面忙于配合上面的意思叼盘。所以上面下定决心要政策转向完全没有阻力。当年从百花齐放百家争鸣到反右倾也不过几个月。", "timestamp": 1653057484}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 128931, "create_time": 1653058077, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Carol: 那你怎么解释大跃进，文化大革命……你假设了“上面”总是理性的，总是正确的，这显然不成立", "timestamp": 1653058077}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 129013, "create_time": 1653060379, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Francis: 上面当然不全是理性的，但是说上面只图虚名的话又明显不符合中国在很多领域（如军事装备发展）的行事逻辑，面子和里子做选择时大多数时候选择了后者。", "timestamp": 1653060379}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 129021, "create_time": 1653060631, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "申论高分玩家游戏", "timestamp": 1653060631}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 129665, "create_time": 1653097057, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯，你看你自己也说了“大多数时候”，你怎么知道动态清零不属于那些“少数时候”呢。", "timestamp": 1653097057}], "create_time": 1653052553, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653060631, "likenum": 9, "n_attentions": 9, "n_comments": 19, "pid": 45096, "poll": null, "reply": 19, "text": "每年的GDP都在增长\n## 有没有可能是国家玩的统计游戏？\n## 就算每年在增长，这一定表示人民生活水平提高了吗？\n最近政府一系列不靠谱的行为已经开始反思这个问题了\n答应了不封城，就提出“静默管理”\n“主动静默”\n“公